    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 15 f — Baldorhynchus tedeschii Bellò & Osella sp. n. holotype ♀ from “ Tampa del Ranzù, N ° 3 Lo, 670 m, Dosso Ranzone, Concesio, Brescia ”: 15 — habitus, dorsal view (scale bar: 1 mm); 15 a—habitus, lateral view; 15 b— rostrum, lateral view; 15 c—pronotum; 15 d—elytra punctuation; 15 e—funicle and club; 15 f—spermatheca." ;
